    <figcaption data-lang="en">
      <b>Six layers, one Earth, two centuries.</b>
      Read top to bottom: orbit, atmosphere, sea surface, sea floor, land
      surface, subterranean. Mackinder's 1904 Pivot Area is drawn as a faint
      grey palimpsest inside the land layer — both as homage and as the layer
      his framework actually addressed. Each band has its own chokepoint set
      and its own resource. The thesis is no longer "who controls the
      Heartland controls the world"; it is "whoever holds chokepoints across
      the most layers controls the most." America's <em>underground empire</em>
      (Farrell &amp; Newman, 2023) sits on cables, dollar clearing, chip
      design, cloud compute. China's countergrip sits on rare earths, refined
      metals, and the LEO race. Both are weaponizing interdependence; neither
      is winning cleanly.
      <span class="legend-line">
        <span class="legend-swatch swatch-us"></span>
        <span><b>US chokepoints</b> — chip design + EUV access + dollar clearing + Loudoun cables.</span>
      </span>
      <span class="legend-line">
        <span class="legend-swatch swatch-cn"></span>
        <span><b>China chokepoints</b> — refined gallium, graphite, rare earths, cobalt route via DRC, NSR shipping with Russia.</span>
      </span>
    </figcaption>

    <figcaption data-lang="zh">
      <b>六层、一个地球、两个世纪。</b>
      从上到下读：轨道、大气、海面、海底、地表、地下。麦金德 1904 年的
      Pivot Area 在地表层里以浅灰浮影呈现——既是致敬，也是把他的框架
      安回它真正适用的那一层。每层都有自己的咽喉点、自己的资源。
      论断已经不是「谁控制 Heartland 谁控制世界」，而是「谁能在更多
      层叠加咽喉点谁控制更多」。美国的<em>"地下帝国"</em>（Farrell &amp;
      Newman, 2023）建在海底光缆、美元清算、芯片设计、云计算之上；
      中国的反制建在稀土、精炼金属、刚果钴线、与俄合作的北方海航线上。
      两边都在 weaponize interdependence，两边都没有干净地赢。
      <span class="legend-line">
        <span class="legend-swatch swatch-us"></span>
        <span><b>美国咽喉</b>——芯片设计 + EUV 准入 + 美元清算 + Loudoun 海缆。</span>
